      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.AsyncDemoBase",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.AsyncDemoBase.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Base class for asynchronous demonstrations using Task and CancellationToken.\nIdeal for complex asynchronous logic, awaiting multiple operations, or integrating with Task-based APIs.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Chobitech.DemoKit.AsyncDemoManager.yml",
      "output": {
