        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.AsyncDemoManager",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.AsyncDemoManager.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Manages the execution lifecycle of an <xref href=\"Chobitech.DemoKit.AsyncDemoBase\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nIt handles task cancellation using <xref href=\"System.Threading.CancellationTokenSource\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and\nensures that lifecycle hooks are called in the correct order.</p>\n"
    },
    {
