      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.BaseDrawer.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A base component that provides side-drawer functionality.\nIt handles UI animations, positioning with margins, and state transitions (open/close).</p>\n"
    },
