      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.CoroutineDemoBase",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.CoroutineDemoBase.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Base class for demonstrations using Unity Coroutines (IEnumerator).\nSuitable for tasks that are tightly integrated with the Unity lifecycle or for users\nwho prefer the standard StartCoroutine pattern.</p>\n"
