      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.CoroutineDemoManager",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.CoroutineDemoManager.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Manages the execution lifecycle of a <xref href=\"Chobitech.DemoKit.CoroutineDemoBase\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nIt handles starting and stopping Unity Coroutines and ensures that lifecycle hooks\nlike <xref href=\"Chobitech.DemoKit.DemoBase.OnDemoCompleted\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and <xref href=\"Chobitech.DemoKit.CoroutineDemoBase.OnDemoCanceled\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> are invoked.</p>\n"
    },
