      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.DemoLogArea.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Manages the log display area within the DemoKit.\nHandles log updates, auto-scroll behavior, and coordination with a <xref href=\"Chobitech.DemoKit.DemoLogArea.BaseDrawer\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> for UI transitions.</p>\n"
    },
