      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.DemoManagerBase",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.DemoManagerBase.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Abstract base class for managing the execution lifecycle of a demonstration.\nIt abstracts the differences between Task-based and Coroutine-based execution,\nproviding a unified interface for the orchestrator.</p>\n"
    },
