      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.GlobalDemoInfo",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.GlobalDemoInfo.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A ScriptableObject that stores global configuration and metadata for the entire DemoKit system.\nIt centralizes information like titles, icons, and shared rich text color tags.</p>\n"
    },
