      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.IndividualDemoInfo.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A ScriptableObject that holds general information about an individual demonstration.\nThis is typically used to store metadata such as the demo's title and a detailed description\nfor display in the UI.</p>\n"
