      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.RectTransformCachedMonoBehaviour",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.RectTransformCachedMonoBehaviour.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A base class for MonoBehaviours that frequently access their <xref href=\"UnityEngine.RectTransform\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nIt caches the RectTransform component during the Awake phase to improve performance\nby avoiding repeated GetComponent calls.</p>\n"
