      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.ScrollTextArea",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.ScrollTextArea.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A UI component that provides a scrollable text area with optional title support.\nIt handles automatic/manual scrolling, text wrapping configurations, and detects user interaction\nthrough <xref href=\"Chobitech.DemoKit.UserScrollDetector\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and <xref href=\"Chobitech.DemoKit.UserScrollBarTouchDetector\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
