      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.UserScrollBarTouchDetector",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.UserScrollBarTouchDetector.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Detects touch or click interactions specifically for a scroll bar.\nImplements Unity's EventSystem interfaces to track the pressing state,\nwhich is useful for pausing auto-scroll behavior when the user interacts with the UI.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Chobitech.DemoKit.UserScrollDetector.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
