      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.UserScrollDetector",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.UserScrollDetector.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Detects user-initiated scrolling or dragging within a UI area.\nThis component triggers an event when the user interacts with a scroll view\nthrough dragging or mouse wheel input, allowing other systems to respond to manual navigation.</p>\n"
